### 获取所有课程
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

### 根据ID获取课程
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courses/COURSE_001
Content-Type: application/json

### 根据专业代码获取课程
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courses/major/CS
Content-Type: application/json

### 添加课程
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "COURSE_TEST",
  "courseName": "测试课程",
  "credit": 3.0,
  "majorCode": "MAJOR_TEST",
  "courseType": "专业必修课"
}

### 更新课程
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/courses/COURSE_TEST
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseName": "更新后的测试课程",
  "credit": 4.0,
  "majorCode": "MAJOR_TEST",
  "courseType": "专业选修课"
}

### 删除课程
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/courses/COURSE_TEST
Content-Type: application/json
